# === Physical Workspace Protection ===
# Ignore massive Bazel caches to prevent indexing lockups
**/bazel-*
**/bazel-bin
**/bazel-out
**/bazel-testlogs
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/.venv

# === AI Hallucination Quarantine ===
# Ignore AI scratchpads so Gemini doesn't learn from agent hallucinations
**/repos/claude-worktrees
**/*.ipynb

# === ANE Artifacts & Datasets ===
# Prevent Gemini from choking on heavy binary blocks and datasets
**/ane_stories110M_ckpt.bin
**/*.mlmodelc
**/training/data/
